---
import Layout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import "../../styles/themes/tools.css";
import "../../styles/pages/articles/article-page.css";
import ContactUs from "../components/ContactUs.astro";

const theme = "resources";
---

<Layout title="GDPR Compliance" theme={theme}>
  <main class="article-page container">

    <!-- ================================
         CUSTOM GDPR STYLES
    ================================ -->
    <style>
      /* Main title green */
      .gdpr-title {
        color: var(--color-primary);
        font-weight: 800;
      }

      /* Section headings green */
      .gdpr-section h2 {
        color: var(--color-primary);
        font-weight: 800;
        margin-top: 2rem;
      }

      /* ICO link red */
      .ico-link {
        color: var(--color-danger) !important;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .ico-link:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      /* Email blue */
      .gdpr-email {
        color: var(--color-info) !important;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .gdpr-email:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
    </style>


    <!-- ================================
         PAGE HEADER
    ================================ -->
    <section style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
      <h1 class="gdpr-title" style="font-size: 2.4rem;">
        GDPR Compliance at Marsal Accountants
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--color-text-light); margin-top: .5rem;">
        Your privacy matters. We are fully compliant with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR).
      </p>
    </section>


    <!-- ================================
         GDPR CONTENT
    ================================ -->
    <section class="gdpr-section" style="margin-bottom: 3rem; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.1rem;">

      <p>
        At Marsal, safeguarding your personal data is a core responsibility. We are fully compliant with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR), which governs how organisations collect, process, and protect personal data across the UK and EU.
      </p>

      <h2>Our Commitment</h2>
      <p>
        We’ve implemented robust technical and organisational measures to ensure your data is handled securely, lawfully, and transparently. Our team is trained to uphold GDPR principles across every interaction.
      </p>

      <h2>GDPR Principles We Follow</h2>
      <ul style="margin-left: 1.2rem;">
        <li>Lawful, fair, and transparent processing</li>
        <li>Purpose-specific data collection</li>
        <li>Data minimisation</li>
        <li>Accuracy and timely updates</li>
        <li>Retention only as long as necessary</li>
        <li>Security and confidentiality</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How Marsal Ensures Compliance</h2>
      <p>
        We maintain detailed records of the data we hold, its origin, and its destination. Our internal policies are regularly reviewed to ensure confidentiality and security at every stage of processing.
      </p>

      <h2>Legal Basis & Consent</h2>
      <p>
        By engaging with Marsal Accountants, you provide consent for us to process your data in line with GDPR. This includes contact details, payroll information, tax identifiers, and other relevant documentation.
      </p>

      <h2>Your Rights</h2>
      <p>
        You have the right to request access to your data, correct inaccuracies, or request deletion—subject to legal retention requirements. We honour these rights promptly and transparently.
      </p>

      <h2>Security & Risk Management</h2>
      <p>
        We continuously assess potential threats and adapt our systems to stay ahead of evolving risks. Our infrastructure is designed to protect your data from unauthorised access, loss, or misuse.
      </p>

      <h2>ICO Registration & Oversight</h2>
      <p>
        Marsal Accountants is registered with the UK Information Commissioner’s Office (ICO) under agreement number <strong>ZC066499</strong>.
      </p>

      <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">
        <a 
          href="https://ico.org.uk/ESDWebPages/Entry/ZC066499" 
          target="_blank" 
          class="ico-link"
        >
          View our ICO registration →
        </a>
      </p>

      <p style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
        In the unlikely event of a data breach, we are legally obligated to notify the ICO within 72 hours and inform affected clients transparently.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        If you have questions about how we handle your data, please contact us at 
        <a href="mailto:info@marsalaccountants.co.uk" class="gdpr-email">
          info@marsalaccountants.co.uk
        </a>.
      </p>

      <p>
        This statement is reviewed regularly to reflect regulatory updates and client feedback. As our services evolve, so will our commitment to data privacy and protection.
      </p>

    </section>


    <!-- ================================
         SERVICES CAROUSEL
    ================================ -->
    <style>
      .services-carousel-section {
        margin-top: 4rem;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .carousel-heading {
        font-size: 2rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        color: var(--color-text);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }

      .carousel-container {
        width: 100%;
        overflow: hidden;
        position: relative;
        padding: 20px 0;
        pointer-events: auto;
      }

      .carousel-track {
        display: flex;
        gap: 20px;
        animation: scroll 40s linear infinite;
        will-change: transform;
        pointer-events: auto;
      }

      @keyframes scroll {
        0% { transform: translateX(0); }
        100% { transform: translateX(calc(-240px * 9)); }
      }

      .service-slide {
        flex: 0 0 auto;
        background: var(--color-surface-lighter);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 6px;
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        width: 200px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        border: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
        pointer-events: auto;
      }

      .service-slide:hover {
        transform: translateY(-4px);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-strong);
        border-color: var(--color-primary);
      }

      .service-slide img {
        width: 60px;
        height: 60px;
        object-fit: contain;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }

      .service-slide h4 {
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin: 0;
        text-align: center;
        line-height: 1.4;
      }

      .service-slide a {
        color: var(--color-primary);
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: color 0.2s ease;
        pointer-events: auto;
      }

      .service-slide a:hover {
        color: var(--color-primary-hover);
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
    </style>

    <section class="services-carousel-section">
      <h2 class="carousel-heading">Explore Our Services</h2>
      <div class="section-divider"></div>

      <div class="carousel-container">
        <div class="carousel-track">

          <div class="service-slide">
            <a href="/services/accounting/">
              <img src="/icons/icons/accounts-icon.png">
              <h4>Accounting Services</h4>
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="service-slide">
            <a href="/services/bookkeeping/">
              <img src="/icons/icons/bookkeeping-icon.png">
              <h4>Bookkeeping Services</h4>
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="service-slide">
            <a href="/services/management-accounts/">
              <img src="/icons/icons/mngt-accounts-icon.png">
              <h4>Management Accounts</h4>
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="service-slide">
            <a href="/services/payroll/">
              <img src="/icons/icons/payroll-services-icon.png">
              <h4>Payroll Services</h4>
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="service-slide">
            <a href="/services/property-accounts/">
              <img src="/icons/icons/property-accounts-icon.png">
              <h4>Property Accounts</h4>
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="service-slide">
            <a href="/services/self-assessment-tax-returns/">
              <img src="/icons/icons/self-assessment-tax-returns-icon.png">
              <h4>Self Assessment</h4>
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="service-slide">
            <a href="/services/business-setup/">
              <img src="/icons/icons/starting-new-business-icon.png">
              <h4>Starting New Business</h4>
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="service-slide">
            <a href="/services/tax-investigation/">
              <img src="/icons/icons/tax-investigation-icon.png">
              <h4>Tax Investigation</h4>
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="service-slide">
            <a href="/services/vat/">
              <img src="/icons/icons/value-added-icon.png">
              <h4>VAT Services</h4>
            </a>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>


    <!-- ================================
         CONTACT US
    ================================ -->
    <section style="margin-top: 4rem;">
      <ContactUs />
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>
